page.title: 07MORE HOMES
page.content:
My house is an upstairs house. It has three bedrooms and two rooms downstairs. It has a garden which is quite big.We have not bought our house.I have a bedroom all of my own.We have got chickens and ducks and two rabbits and a shed.My house is made of concrete and it is about 20 yaers old. It is heated with electricity.It has an attic .
My house is a bungalow and my garden has got a lot of grass up to the back of the hedge and the kitchen is very small so I can hardly get into it.My brother's bedroom is always a mess. My bedroom is always tidy.
